https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#Feature.name: Feature
https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#Feature.description: A Feature object represents a spatially bounded thing

https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#FeatureCo.name: Feature Collection
https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#FeatureCo.description: A FeatureCollection object has a member with the name "features". The value of "features" is a JSON array. Each element of the array is a Feature object

https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#GeometryC.name: Geometry Collection
https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#GeometryC.description: A GeoJSON object with type "GeometryCollection" is a Geometry object. A GeometryCollection has a member with the name "geometries".  The value of "geometries" is an array.  Each element of this array is a Geometry object

https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#LineStrin.name: Line String
https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#LineStrin.description: A geometry whose coordinates are an array of two or more positions

https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#MultiLine.name: Multi LineString
https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#MultiLine.description: A geometry whose coordinates are an array of Line Strings

https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#MultiPoin.name: Multi Point
https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#MultiPoin.description: A geometry whose coordinates are an array positions

https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#MultiPoly.name: Multi Polygon
https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#MultiPoly.description: A geometry whose coordinates are an array of Polygon coordinate arrays

https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#Point.name: Point
https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#Point.description: A geometry whose coordinates are a single position

https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#Polygon.name: Polygon
https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#Polygon.description: A geometry whose coordinates are a linear ring

https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#bbox.name: bounding box
https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#bbox.description: A rectangle with the smallest measure (area) within which all the coordinate point of the Feature lie

https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#coordinat.name: coordinates
https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#coordinat.description: A property indicating a set of two or more numbers used to determine the position of a point, line, curve, or plane in a space of a given dimension with respect to a system of lines or other fixed references.

https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#propertie.name: properties
https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#propertie.description: Indicates a collection of properties for a Feature

https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#type.name: geometry type
https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#type.description: Indicates a specialised form of a subject class
